# Copy to .env (or set in your host's environment) and adjust.

# Where the app stores accounts, imported tests, and score history.
# OPTIONAL: if unset, the app already defaults to a persistent location in the
# home directory (~/sat-prep-data) that survives redeploys — so you usually
# DON'T need to set this. Only set it to force an explicit location.
# Example on Hostinger (adjust the username): /home/u123456789/sat-data
# SAT_DATA_DIR=/home/CHANGE_ME/sat-data
